{"tid":265463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人欠包容  錫克教徒倡容許學童帶刀上學","createTime":"2017-05-31T15:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T15:43:59.000Z","uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c2df085f59dbb0f1f736aa6320b8b3d82586f7","tid":265463,"uid":82646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSudMbbhYMfcd7wUncPRizMv_uUc8G3Kqs9kk3y3sjGUhvvDkTT2w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn1.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSudMbbhYMfcd7wUncPRizMv_uUc8G3Kqs9kk3y3sjGUhvvDkTT2w&h=fcba064f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n信奉錫克教 美國男童獲准帶刀上學<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1139353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1139353&d=sUc5KZ8H5SHklGhWMu8F%2BxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=f2554c96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1139353&h=31148d21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1139353</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國校園事件頻傳，因此許多地區嚴禁學生攜帶槍械武器上學，華盛頓州1名信奉錫克教（Sikh）的男童，被允許能以宗教信仰為由帶刀上學。<br />\n<br />\n錫克教徒在身上佩帶聖刀喀爾潘（Kirpan）以象徵勇氣，《今日美國》報導，華盛頓州奧本（Auburn）的吉爾多雷小學（Gildo Rey Elementary）有1名家裡信奉錫克教的男童，透過家長向學校協調，希望能佩帶聖刀上學。<br />\n<br />\n在學區主管查詢過州政府及聯邦政府的法條後，得知在某些情況下，華盛頓州的武器「零容忍」政策得允許特例存在，而且許多同樣信奉錫克教的教職員工及學生，同樣配帶聖刀多年且沒有發生任何問題。<br />\n<br />\n針對這次案例，學區副主管萊恩（Ryan Foster）表示學區允許男童可以佩帶聖刀，但必須藏在衣服內不得外露，學區的做法同時尊重信仰，也維護了其他學生的安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nps 1985年印度航空182號班機遭受炸彈襲擊，機上乘客連機組人員共329人全部遇難。事後調查發現此次襲擊為錫克教恐怖分子策劃。"},{"pid":"cce94a58103a8351334baeb47a9953c5a34617a7","tid":265463,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}